ull, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011433, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O my God, the beseechers have stood at Your Door, the poor have resorted to Your refuge, and the ship of the needy have cast anchor near the coast of the sea of Your Magnanimity and Generosity, hoping for permission to enter the yard of Your Mercy and Favor. O my God, If You, in this holy month, will have mercy upon none but those who sincerely observe fasting and do acts of worship to You, who will then stand for the sinful and the negligent then they sink in the ocean of their sins and offenses?", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Parwardigaar yeh saael (sawaali) Tere darwaaze par khade hai aur un faqiro’n ne Teri baargah mein panah le li hai, miskeeno ka safina'e muraad Tere saahil jood o karam par thaiyr gaya hai aur maqsad yeh hai keh badh kar Teri baargah'e rehmat o neymat tak pohonch jaaye. Khudaaya! Agar Tu is mohtaram mahine mein sirf un par rahem karega jo apne seyaam o qayaam (roze aur namaaz) mein mukhlis ho to us gunah-gaar aur taqseer-waar ka kya hoga jo apne gunaho’n mein dooba huwa hai?", "Urdu": "اے پروردگار! یہ سائل تیرے دروازہ پر کھڑے ہیں اور ان فقراء نے تیری بارگاہ میں پناہ لے لی ہے مسکینوں کا سفینہ مراد ٹھر گیا ہے تیرے ساحل جود و کرم پر اور مقصد یہ کہ بڑھ کر تیری بارگاہ رحمت و نعمت تک پہنچ جائیں۔ خدایا! اگر تو اس محترم مہینہ میں صرف ان پر رحم کرے گا جو اپنے صیام و قیام میں مخلص ہوں تو اس گناہگار اور تقصیر وار کا کیا ہو گا جو اپنے گناہوں میں ڈوبا ہوا ہے؟ ", "RArabic": "ILAAHEE WA-QAFAS SAA'e LOONA BE-BAABE-KA WA LAA ZAL FOQA-RAA-O BE-JANAABE-KA WA WA-QA-FAT SAFEENA-TUL MASAA-KEENE A’LAA SAAHE-LE BAHRE JOODE-KA WA KARAME-KA YARJOO-NAL JAWAA-ZA ILAA SAAHA-TE RAHMATE-KA WA NE’MATE-KA ILAAHEE IN KUNTA LAA TAR-HAMO FEE HAA-ZASH SHAH-RISH SHAREE-FE ILLAA MAN AKH-LASA LAKA FEE SE-YAAME-HI FA-MANIL LIL MUZNE-BIL MOQAS-SERE IZAA GHARE-QA FEE BAHRE ZONOO-BE-HI WA AA-SAAME-HI.", "ArabicText1": "اِلٰهِيْ وَقَفَ السَّائِلُوْنَ بِبَابِكَ وَلَاذَ الْفُقَرَاءُ بِجَنَابِكَ وَ وَقَفَتْ سَفِيْنَةُ الْمَسَاكِيْنِ عَلٰى سَاحِلِ بَحْرِ جُوْدِكَ وَكَرَمِكَ يَرْجُوْنَ الْجَوَازَ اِلٰى سَاحَةِ رَحْمَتِكَ وَنِعْمَتِكَ اِلٰهِيْ اِنْ كُنْتَ لَا تَرْحَمُ فِيْ هٰذَا الشَّهْرِ الشَّرِيْفِ اِلَّا مَنْ اَخْلَصَ لَكَ فِيْ صِيَامِهٖ وَقِيَامِهٖ فَمَنِ لِّلْمُذْنِبِ الْمُقَصِّرِ اِذَا غَرِقَ فِيْ بَحْرِ ذُنُوْبِهٖ وَآثَامِهٖ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011434, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O my God, if you have mercy upon none but the obedient to You, who will then stand for the disobedient? If You accept none but those who do acts of worship to You, who will then stand for the negligent? O my God, the observers of fasting have won, the doers of acts of worship to You have prospered, and those who act sincerely have been saved. But we, Your sinful servants, beseech Your mercy; so, (please do) have mercy upon us, release us from the chastisement of Hellfire, out of Your pardon, and forgive our sins, in the name of Your mercy. O most Merciful of all those who show mercy!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Khudaaya! Agar Tu sirf ita’at guzaaro’n par rahem karega to maasiyyat-kaaro’n (na-farmaano) ka kya hoga? Aur agar Tu sirf ba-amal afraad ke amaal qabool karega to kotaahi karne waalo’n ka anjaam kya hoga? Khudaaya! Roze-daaro’n ne faaiyda kama liya aur namaaziyo’n ne kaamyaabi haasil kar li aur mukhlis najaat pa-gaye, ab ham Tere gunah-gaar bande baaqi rahe gaye hai, Tu ham par bhi apni maher-baani kar aur apne afwo se hamein bhi aatish-e-Jahannam se azaad kar, hamaare gunah bakhsh de apni rehmat se, ay sabse ziyadah rahem karne waale.", "Urdu": "خدایا! اگر تو صرف اطاعت گذاروں پر رحم کرے گا تو معصیت  کاروں کا کیا ہو گا؟ اور اگر تو صرف با عمل افراد کے اعمال قبول کرے گا تو کوتاہی کرنے والوں کا انجام کیا ہو گا؟ خدایا! روزہ داروں نے فائدہ کما لیا اور نمازیوں نے کامیابی حاصل کر لی اور مخلص نجات پا گئے اب ہم تیرے گناہگار بندے باقی رہ گئے ہیں تو ہم پر بھی اپنی مہربانی کر اور اپنے عفو سے ہمیں بھی آتش جہنم سے آزاد کر، ہمارے گناہ بخش دے اپنی رحمت سے اے سب سے زیادہ رحم کرنے والے۔", "RArabic": "ILAAHEE IN KUNTA LAA TAR-HAMO ILLAL MOTEE-EE’NA FA-MAN LIL-AA’SEENA WA IN KUNTA LAA TAQ-BALO ILLAA MENAL AA’ME-LEENA FA-MANIL LIL-MO-QASSE-REENA ILAAHEE RABE-HAS SAA'e MOONA WA NAJAA AL-MUKHLE-SOONA WA NAHNO A’BEEDO-KAL MUZNE-BOONA FAR-HAMNAA BE-RAHMATE-KA WA’TIQ-NAA MENAN NAARE BA-A’FWE-KA WAGH-FIR-LANAA ZONOO-BANAA BE-RAHMATE-KA YAA AR-HAMAR RAAHE-MEEN.", "ArabicText1": "اِلٰهِيْ اِنْ كُنْتَ لَا تَرْحَمُ اِلَّا الْمُطِيْعِيْنَ فَمَنْ لِلْعَاصِيْنَ وَاِنْ كُنْتَ لَا تَقْبَلُ اِلَّا مِنَ الْعَامِلِيْنَ فَمَنِ لِّلْمُقَصِّرِيْنَ اِلٰهِيْ رَبِحَ الصَّائِمُوْنَ وَفَازَ الْقَائِمُوْنَ وَنَجَا اَلْمُخْلِصُوْنَ وَنَحْنُ عَبِيْدُكَ الْمُذْنِبُوْنَ فَارْحَمْنَا بِرَحْمَتِكَ وَاعْتِقْنَا مِنَ النَّارِ بَعَفْوِكَ وَاغْفِرْ لَنَا ذُنُوْبَنَا بِرَحْمَتِكَ يَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText